{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onItemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"MenuModelRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModelRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO12MenuModelRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}]}],"name":"flags"},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal handler to call"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"code":"itemsChanged","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The only changes that can occur to a menu is that items are removed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"or added.  Items may not change (except by being removed and added","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"back in the same location).  This signal is capable of describing","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"both of those changes (at the same time)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal means that starting at the index "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"position"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"removed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"items were removed and "},{"code":"added","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" items were added in their place.  If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"removed","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is zero then only items were added.  If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"added"},{"text":" is zero","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"then only items were removed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As an example, if the menu contains items a, b, c, d (in that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"order) and the signal (2, 1, 3) occurs then the new composition of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the menu will be a, b, _, _, _, d (with each _ representing some","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"new item).","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Signal handlers may query the model (particularly the added items)"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and expect to see the results of the modification that is being","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"reported.  The signal is emitted after the modification.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"code":"items-changed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" signal"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuRef\/MenuModelProtocol-Implementations"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/menuref\/onitemschanged(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Emitted when a change has occurred to the menu."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuRef\/onItemsChanged(flags:handler:)"},"metadata":{"extendedModule":"GIO","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"title":"onItemsChanged(flags:handler:)","externalID":"s:3GIO17MenuModelProtocolPAAE14onItemsChanged5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bC3RefV_S3itctF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO7MenuRefV","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"onItemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO12MenuModelRefV","text":"MenuModelRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MenuModel":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MenuModel"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModel","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/menumodel","title":"MenuModel","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"MenuModel","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GMenuModel"},{"type":"text","text":" represents the contents of a menu — an ordered list of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"menu items. The items are associated with actions, which can be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"activated through them. Items can be grouped in sections, and may","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"have submenus associated with them. Both items and sections usually","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"have some representation data, such as labels or icons. The type of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the associated action (ie whether it is stateful, and what kind of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"state it has) can influence the representation of the item."}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MenuRef/onItemsChanged(flags:handler:)":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Emitted when a change has occurred to the menu.","type":"text"}],"title":"onItemsChanged(flags:handler:)","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuRef\/onItemsChanged(flags:handler:)","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/menuref\/onitemschanged(flags:handler:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onItemsChanged"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO1